data.description: Assumable VA Loan under 3%! Spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is conveniently located in the Natomas Meadows community of Sacramento. The open floor-plan is ideal for entertaining with family and friends. Bedroom and Full bath downstairs is perfect for guests! Amazing finishing touches throughout the home. Built by Lennar. The kitchen includes a large quartz island, stainless steel appliances, tons of cabinet space and a walk-in pantry. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet and dual vanities in the bath. The garage is in the rear of the house with entry from the alley. This home is close to the association's amenities, including a pool and clubhouse. Don't miss out on this opportunity.
